@startuml Legend
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false

title <size:16><b>Flow Diagram Legend</b></size>

legend
    |= Symbol |= Meaning |= Color |
    | <#90EE90> Start/Success | Start point or successful operation | Green |
    | <#FFD700> Process | Normal processing step | Yellow |
    | <#FFF9C4> Decision | Decision point / condition check | Light Yellow |
    | <#FFE082> Warning | Warning state or retry | Orange |
    | <#FF6B6B> Error/Stop | Error state or stop point | Red |
    | <#E3F2FD> Activity | Regular activity block | Light Blue |
    | <#87CEEB> Active State | Active/running state | Sky Blue |
endlegend

@enduml